# AVKitError.Code.contentDisallowedByProfile

**Case**

An installed profile restricts access to this content.

## Declaration

```swift
case contentDisallowedByProfile
```

## Discussion

The user can’t override this restriction by entering the device passcode, but they may be able to override it in the Settings app.

## Error Codes

- **AVKitError.Code.unknown**: An unknown error.
- **AVKitError.Code.contentRatingUnknown**: The media content rating is missing or unrecognized.
- **AVKitError.Code.contentDisallowedByPasscode**: A restriction disallows access to this content, but the user can override the restriction by entering the device passcode.
- **AVKitError.Code.pictureInPictureStartFailed**: The system failed to start Picture in Picture.
